### Register User - Password Mismatch (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Lỗi Test",
  "email": "error@example.com",
  "password": "Correct123456",
  "confirmPassword": "Wrong123456"
}

### Register User - Short Password (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Lỗi Test",
  "email": "error2@example.com",
  "password": "Short12",
  "confirmPassword": "Short12"
}

### Register User - Invalid Email (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Lỗi Test",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "ValidPass123",
  "confirmPassword": "ValidPass123"
}

### Register User - Empty Fields (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "",
  "email": "",
  "password": "",
  "confirmPassword": ""
}
